[SN]TITLE[SN]
Cash calendar - tips for September

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Buying a car and travelling by train can be considerably cheaper by considering a few simple tips, an advice service says.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
1 September 2016 Last updated at 10:49 BST
The BBC News website asked the independent Money Advice Service to deliver a calendar of month-by-month tips for those trying to keep their personal finances in order.
Kat Hodgkinson, from the service, says that September is a good time to negotiate when buying a car, and there are potentially cheaper options when travelling on public transport.
